Hi Sarah! I'm having a bit of trouble with my recent order.

I’m sorry to hear that. May I have your name, please, so I can assist you better?

Sure! My name is John Doe.

Thank you, John! Could you also provide me with your phone number, please?

Yes, it's five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Great! And could I have your email address as well?

Of course! It's john.doe@example.com.

I received the wrong drink. I ordered a lager, but I got a stout instead.

I apologize for the mix-up. I will make sure to resolve this for you. Thank you for your time, John, and have a fantastic day!
